in the holidays?

212
00:22:33,552 --> 00:22:35,429
A few

213
00:22:35,510 --> 00:22:41,558
Create something extempore,
then we'll consider you a poet

214
00:22:42,001 --> 00:22:44,661
Extempore?

215
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:46,792
- Shall I?
- Yes

216
00:22:49,922 --> 00:22:52,140
