These shameless glances, these crude remarks

826
01:32:17,388 --> 01:32:23,013
These wilting bodies, these ailing faces

827
01:32:23,327 --> 01:32:34,072
Where are those who claim to be
proud of India?

828
01:32:40,711 --> 01:32:46,465
Old men have passed through here,
young men, too

829
